    <briefdescription>
<para>A RAII Guard for GLFW. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class makes sure that GLFW is properly initialized when an instance is created and terminated when this instance is destroyed.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ulink url="https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/raii.html">https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/language/raii.html</ulink> </para>
